text: Ainsley was super awesome and funny. Lucky to have found him to host our 20 years wedding anniversary celebrations. Everyone enjoyed the evening - absolutely perfect.

We are thrilled to have engaged the remarkable talents of Ainsley as the emcee for our highly anticipated Annual Dinner & Dance event. His dedication to delivering excellence is palpable in every aspect of his service. Ainsley's innate ability to captivate and energize the audience elevates the entire atmosphere, transforming the evening into an unforgettable experience for all attendees. His seamless blend of professionalism, and wit ensures that every moment is infused with excitement and enjoyment. We extend our heartfelt gratitude to Ainsley for his outstanding contribution in making our event a resounding success. Well done, Ainsley!

Ainsley hosted our wedding in Hunter Valley and in a wide open farm space. He did an amazing job from giving us ideas to make sequencing smoother than our own plan, probing the vibes we wanted as well as impromptu fillers (that were required due to logistics of a DIY wedding). There was never a moment of awkwardness, he lifted the mood of the crowd.

Overall, he delivered a thoroughly enjoyable time for all the guests and we had lots of positive feedback. I would not hesitate to have him host again.

Engaging Ainsley Chong as our emcee for our annual dinner was the best decision made! He was very engaging, funny, and everyone loved him! Especially his energy, the dance and music was fantastic! Having him as our emcee really gave us a lot less things to worry about as he is so reliable. Ainsley is able to speak in many languages, which allowed him to converse with both the local and foreigner workers from different country with more engagement and entertainment.

Thanks so much for bringing much fun and laughter. It was truly beyond our expectations. Highly recommended!!!

It was an extremely pleasant experience to engage Ainsley as our emcee for our wedding. He is professional, places himself in our shoes and understands what we need. Would definitely recommend him to anyone who wishes to engage him as your emcee!
